"{\"uid\": \"jamaicaobserver.com-2024-07-31-low-emissions-food-leaves-paris-olympics-athletes-craving-meat\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"PARIS, France (AFP) - An ambition from Paris Olympics organisers to cut the carbon footprint of catering at this year's eco-friendly games has run into a problem - the huge appetites of meat-loving athletes.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 207, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7, \"end\": 13, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.999991547985949, \"rank\": 7.212602025493104e-06, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 39, \"end\": 53, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"PARIS\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 5}, {\"ngram\": \"AFP\", \"from\": 15, \"to\": 18}, {\"ngram\": \"An ambition\", \"from\": 22, \"to\": 33}, {\"ngram\": \"the carbon footprint\", \"from\": 72, \"to\": 92}, {\"ngram\": \"this year's eco-friendly games\", \"from\": 108, \"to\": 138}, {\"ngram\": \"a problem\", \"from\": 152, \"to\": 161}, {\"ngram\": \"the huge appetites\", \"from\": 164, \"to\": 182}, {\"ngram\": \"meat-loving athletes\", \"from\": 186, \"to\": 206}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At a trial run at the Olympics village restaurant in June, games supremo Tony Estanguet stressed how Paris 2024 was aiming to cut the average carbon emissions per meal in half compared to previous Olympics by offering more vegetarian food.\", \"from\": 209, \"to\": 448, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 282, \"end\": 296, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tony Estanguet\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\"}, {\"begin\": 310, \"end\": 320, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.050099169433729e-17, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a trial run\", \"from\": 212, \"to\": 223}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics village restaurant\", \"from\": 227, \"to\": 258}, {\"ngram\": \"June\", \"from\": 262, \"to\": 266}, {\"ngram\": \"the average carbon emissions\", \"from\": 339, \"to\": 367}, {\"ngram\": \"meal\", \"from\": 372, \"to\": 376}, {\"ngram\": \"half\", \"from\": 380, \"to\": 384}, {\"ngram\": \"previous Olympics\", \"from\": 397, \"to\": 414}, {\"ngram\": \"more vegetarian food\", \"from\": 427, \"to\": 447}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Promising not to disappoint visitors to a country famed for its gastronomy, the organising committee also took on several Michelin-starred chefs as advisors to work alongside its food contractor, French multinational Sodexo.\", \"from\": 450, \"to\": 674, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 572, \"end\": 588, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michelin_Guide\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Michelin-starred\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michelin_Guide\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michelin_Guide\"}, {\"begin\": 646, \"end\": 652, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9091827261395086, \"rank\": 0.0924180801942941, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 667, \"end\": 673, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodexo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sodexo\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodexo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodexo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"visitors\", \"from\": 478, \"to\": 486}, {\"ngram\": \"a country\", \"from\": 490, \"to\": 499}, {\"ngram\": \"its gastronomy\", \"from\": 510, \"to\": 524}, {\"ngram\": \"the organising committee\", \"from\": 526, \"to\": 550}, {\"ngram\": \"advisors\", \"from\": 598, \"to\": 606}, {\"ngram\": \"its food contractor\", \"from\": 625, \"to\": 644}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the first few days in the village, located in a deprived suburb north of Paris, saw demands for more meat, eggs and bigger helpings as athletes looked to replenish themselves after gruelling competitions or gym sessions.\", \"from\": 676, \"to\": 900, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 753, \"end\": 758, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4920346445153651e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the first few days\", \"from\": 680, \"to\": 698}, {\"ngram\": \"the village\", \"from\": 702, \"to\": 713}, {\"ngram\": \"a deprived suburb\", \"from\": 726, \"to\": 743}, {\"ngram\": \"demands\", \"from\": 764, \"to\": 771}, {\"ngram\": \"more meat\", \"from\": 776, \"to\": 785}, {\"ngram\": \"eggs\", \"from\": 787, \"to\": 791}, {\"ngram\": \"bigger helpings\", \"from\": 796, \"to\": 811}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 815, \"to\": 823}, {\"ngram\": \"gruelling competitions\", \"from\": 861, \"to\": 883}, {\"ngram\": \"gym sessions\", \"from\": 887, \"to\": 899}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The only issue would be the food shortages,\\\" swimmer Julio Horrego from Honduras told AFP on Monday when asked about life in the village.\", \"from\": 902, \"to\": 1040, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 975, \"end\": 983, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Honduras\", \"score\": 0.9999998642797528, \"rank\": 1.3570956919437893e-07, \"text\": \"Honduras\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Honduras\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Honduras\"}, {\"begin\": 989, \"end\": 992, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"score\": 0.9999996475840528, \"rank\": 3.5028708899544526e-07, \"text\": \"AFP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The only issue\", \"from\": 903, \"to\": 917}, {\"ngram\": \"the food shortages\", \"from\": 927, \"to\": 945}, {\"ngram\": \"Julio Horrego\", \"from\": 956, \"to\": 969}, {\"ngram\": \"Monday\", \"from\": 996, \"to\": 1002}, {\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 1020, \"to\": 1024}, {\"ngram\": \"the village\", \"from\": 1028, \"to\": 1039}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's a bit surprising.\\\"\", \"from\": 1041, \"to\": 1065, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Horrego, who says he eats up to 5,000 calories per day, said he turned up for breakfast at 10:30am on Sunday only to find there were no eggs left.\", \"from\": 1067, \"to\": 1213, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Horrego\", \"from\": 1067, \"to\": 1074}, {\"ngram\": \"up to 5,000 calories\", \"from\": 1093, \"to\": 1113}, {\"ngram\": \"day\", \"from\": 1118, \"to\": 1121}, {\"ngram\": \"breakfast\", \"from\": 1145, \"to\": 1154}, {\"ngram\": \"10:30am\", \"from\": 1158, \"to\": 1165}, {\"ngram\": \"Sunday\", \"from\": 1169, \"to\": 1175}, {\"ngram\": \"no eggs\", \"from\": 1200, \"to\": 1207}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If you arrive a bit late, then there are not enough,\\\" he said at the entrance to the village which is buzzing with activity and can house 10,500 athletes in its roughly 40 low-rise towers.\", \"from\": 1215, \