\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lucas_Industries\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lucas_Industries\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the size\", \"from\": 1619, \"to\": 1627}, {\"ngram\": \"helpings\", \"from\": 1631, \"to\": 1639}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"At the start there were not very big portions for people, but it's improved now,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1662, \"to\": 1753, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the start\", \"from\": 1666, \"to\": 1675}, {\"ngram\": \"very big portions\", \"from\": 1691, \"to\": 1708}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1713, \"to\": 1719}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The food hall includes six different dining areas offering meals from around the globe, with half of the 50 dishes available each day being 100 per cent vegetarian.\", \"from\": 1755, \"to\": 1919, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The food hall\", \"from\": 1755, \"to\": 1768}, {\"ngram\": \"six different dining areas\", \"from\": 1778, \"to\": 1804}, {\"ngram\": \"meals\", \"from\": 1814, \"to\": 1819}, {\"ngram\": \"the globe\", \"from\": 1832, \"to\": 1841}, {\"ngram\": \"half\", \"from\": 1848, \"to\": 1852}, {\"ngram\": \"the 50 dishes\", \"from\": 1856, \"to\": 1869}, {\"ngram\": \"cent\", \"from\": 1903, \"to\": 1907}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We enjoy our greens, so it's not a problem,\\\" Canadian beach volleyball player Sophie Bukovec said as she left the complex.\", \"from\": 1921, \"to\": 2044, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1967, \"end\": 1975, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.9664043286691234, \"rank\": 0.034758428537329154, \"text\": \"Canadian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}, {\"begin\": 2000, \"end\": 2006, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sophie_McKay\", \"score\": 0.9542450535353773, \"rank\": 0.0478538491778530