m\": \"previous editions\", \"from\": 2547, \"to\": 2564}, {\"ngram\": \"some critics\", \"from\": 2574, \"to\": 2586}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The housing complex, which will be converted into apartments after the games, was built without air-conditioning and instead has a renewable underfloor geo-thermal cooling and heating system.\", \"from\": 2608, \"to\": 2799, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The housing complex\", \"from\": 2608, \"to\": 2627}, {\"ngram\": \"apartments\", \"from\": 2658, \"to\": 2668}, {\"ngram\": \"the games\", \"from\": 2675, \"to\": 2684}, {\"ngram\": \"air-conditioning\", \"from\": 2704, \"to\": 2720}, {\"ngram\": \"a renewable underfloor geo-thermal cooling\", \"from\": 2737, \"to\": 2779}, {\"ngram\": \"heating system\", \"from\": 2784, \"to\": 2798}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some teams such as the US, Great Britain, the Netherlands or France have opted to install portable coolers for their athletes, but others are having to do without, with temperatures on Tuesday and Wednesday above 30 degrees Celsius (95 F) with high humidity.\", \"from\": 2801, \"to\": 3059, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2824, \"end\": 2826, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_dollar\", \"score\": 0.852192089674953, \"rank\": 0.1734442193829809, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_dollar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_dollar\"}, {\"begin\": 2828, \"end\": 2841, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.999991011655234, \"rank\": 8.973886295696272e-06, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 2847, \"end\": 2858, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.999999995545295, \"rank\": 4.362085576730451e-09, \"text\": \"Netherlands\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"